1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Myth: MIT tested 41 AI models on 11,000 real tasks. The "good enough" problem is worse than you think. only helps power users.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Why people believe it: the tools look complicated at first glance.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Fact: MIT tested 41 AI models on 11,000 real tasks. The "good enough" problem is worse than you think. works best when you start with one simple repeatable task.

4
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Do this today: automate one task that takes more than five minutes.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Follow for daily practical workflows.
